title: Greece Attacks - The Next Assault (2004) (320 kbps mp3)
description:
Greece Attacks - The Next Assault is a double-CD compilation released in 2004 by the Greek magazine Sound & Vision, featuring 32 Greek metal or metal related bands, each band performing one song. This compilation is a sequel to Greece Attacks, a double-LP compilation that was released in 1989 by greek FM Records.
